SdkFolderBuildInfo

public class SdkFolderBuildInfo
extends BuildInfo implements ISdkBuildInfo, IFolderBuildInfo

java.lang.Object
   ↳ com.android.tradefed.build.BuildInfo
     ↳ com.android.tradefed.build.SdkFolderBuildInfo

A IBuildInfo that represents an extracted Android SDK and tests and additional build artifacts that are contained in a local file system directory.
